data.description: Wonderfull newer home located in a quiet neighborhood. Lots of upgrades throughout this home.  It has one level living with charm. Assumable Loan $155,000 %3.625. 25 years left.  Awesome floor plan with efficient use of space. Beautiful knotty alder cabinets throughout the home. Tile in the kitchen and the bathrooms LVP in the living area. Nice master bath that has tile surround shower and walk in closet, also included is a nice storage shed in the back yard. The garage has a hot/cold faucet and is also wired for a 220 volt. There is an RV pad on the south side of the home. It boasts a fully landscaped yard and wonderful views of the Wellsville mountains. The green pastures behind the large .29 acre lot enhances the rural open space feel. The yard is fully finished and has sprinkler system. All appliances are included in the sale. Come check this home out before it gone.
